  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK849">
<l>kāṇātāṟ kāṭṭuvāṉ ṟāṉkāṇāṉ kāṇātāṉ </l>
<l>kaṇṭāṉān tāṉkaṇṭa vāṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>One who would teach a fool will (simply) betray his folly; and the fool would (still) think himself "wise in his own conceit".</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
